connection refused , cannot execute on any known server:
connect the database or start the database

port already in use:
kill the port using: sudo netstat -nlp | grep <portnum>
sudo kill -TERM <--->

broker error:
start kafka

Null pointer exception in saving(in recommendation ms):
do not declare field as null
include all instances of repos in constructor

trusted package issue:
package names of producer and consumer should be same

